Package: geotools
Type: Package
Title: Manipulate and Filter Geospatial Data
Version: 2020.09.11
Author: David Holstius
Maintainer: David Holstius <dholstius@baaqmd.gov>
Description: Provides simplified, user-friendly ways to: filter features spatially (by using a second Spatial object); extract attributes and class members; fortify Spatial data (for ggplot2); promote data frames to Spatial objects; use Google's geocoding API; clip SpatialPolygons (gClip); perform IDW interpolation; and use filter() instead of subset().
LazyData: TRUE
Reverse-Depends: inventory
